{"tid":1895814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[立場新聞］你知道鑽石公主號有港人危殆嗎？","createTime":"2020-02-24T18:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T02:48:26.000Z","uid":49316,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ce447608f77252496af71d111f184ca580adb2bb","tid":1895814,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:28:17.000Z","msg":"仆街政府又唔公佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《【鑽石公主號】4 名確診港人情況特別嚴重　須以人工肺或呼吸機維持生命》這則新聞，即使你不是記者、編輯，都知道是很重要的新聞。<br />\n<br />\n這個數字，來自一個保安局、衞生署細圍吹風會，沒有公開的採訪通知，同事意外撈到。行家說：「全行都在，只欠你們和蘋果。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E8%99%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%B1%E6%AE%86%E5%97%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%2591%25BD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25AE%2586%25E5%2597%258E%2F&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=9b3db4f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%2591%25BD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25AE%2586%25E5%2597%258E%2F&h=1268a912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E8%99%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%B1%E6%AE%86%E5%97%8E/</a>"},{"pid":"59a7fca1f78149878c0ec65cf26db104a74997c9","tid":1895814,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:32:33.000Z","msg":"死link"},{"pid